row.InputSentence1: My professor assigned my class an essay.
row.InputSentence2: By the time I left the classroom, I had forgotten about it.
row.InputSentence3: A few days later, my classmate messaged me to ask if I had done it.
row.InputSentence4: I was so upset because I had totally forgotten!
row.RandomFifthSentenceQuiz1: I was worried about my grade.
row.RandomFifthSentenceQuiz2: I was sure I would get an A if I didn't turn in my essay.
